'''Škola Animiranog Filma''' (ŠAF) is a school of [[animation]] located in [[Čakovec]], [[Croatia]].

The program's intent is not career development, but to promote cognition, imagination, perseverance, cooperation and pride in one's work for children between the ages of 8 and 12 years old. [[Edo Lukman]] has been the head of the school since its founding on February 28, 1975. Since then, over a hundred animated short films have been created by more than 500 children enrolled in the program. ŠAF is an active participant and organizer of many animated [[film festival]]s and workshops.

